assets.name: assets/dc_vNxIsZ-z
assets.description:
This is my first Scene in which I tried to tell a story, not just randomly draw with strokes in Tiltbrush :) (Danny Bittman Becoming a VR Artist Ep. 7)  

#city #futuristic #church #sect #night #cyberpunk #neon #night #environment #hunter

The story:
The soldier’s car broke. He’s close to the futuristic sect town. The wolf follows him. He’s got surveillance towers in front of him, and a city you might never get away from again. . .But he can’t go anywhere else
